text: For those who watched this trailer be warned:  THIS MOVIE IS NOT A COMEDY  watched this movie on the 12/27/17, my overall experience with the movie was great. The actors did amazing (especially Hong Chau), the story was straightforward, but this trailer gives off the impression that this is a comedy. Yes there are a few good funny parts and interactions but it's tough to define this movie into a single genre, but it is definitely not a comedy.  THAT BEING SAID  I wholeheartedly recommend this movie for everyone to see.
